address.desc: Contact information for a page or article element

area.desc: Hyperlink or dead area on an image map

base.desc: Base URL and default target navigable for hyperlinks and forms

blockquote.desc: A section quoted from another source

br.desc: Line break, e.g. in poem or postal address

colgroup.desc: Group of columns in a table

datalist.desc: Container for options for combo box control

div.desc: Generic flow container, or container for name-value groups in dl elements

dl.desc: Association list consisting of zero or more name-value groups

footer.desc: Footer for a page or section

header.desc: Introductory or navigational aids for a page or section

main.desc: Container for the dominant contents of the document

optgroup.desc: Group of options in a list box

option.desc: Option in a list box or combo box control

source.desc: Image source for img or media source for video or audio

tbody.desc: Group of rows in a table

tfoot.desc: Group of footer rows in a table

thead.desc: Group of heading rows in a table

time.desc: Machine-readable equivalent of date- or time-related data
